<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><m>3\times3</m>: It’s 3 groups of 3.</li>
      <li><m>2\times4</m> or <m>4\times2</m>: There were 2 parts and each part had 4 in it.</li>
      <li><m>2\times6</m> or <m>6\times2</m>: There are 2 groups with 6 in each group.</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


